():

1. *Vi* ste zaista divni ljudi. (You are really wonderful people.)
2. *Vi* ste naša nada. (You are our hope.)
3. *Vidi* šta smo napravili. (See what we have done.)
4. *Vidite* da je situacija teška. (You can see that the situation is difficult.)
5. *Videćeš* da će biti sve u redu. (You will see that everything will be okay.)